column3: area-averaged changes over five regions  as simulated by CMIP6 models (individually identifiable) and CMIP5 models (blue)
Data is for the blue and colored circles in Figure 3.11 in the IPCC Working Group 1 Contribution to the Six Assessment Report: Chapter 3
Five regions include Northern Europe, Western and Central Europe, Mediterranean, Sahara/Sahel and West Africa (Iturbide et al., 2020).
Data are only sampled at reconstruction points, pollen-based reconstructed annual mean precipitation (MAP) from Bertlein et al. (2011).
